okeCommandAction Command="{Binding Path=CityLostFocusCommand}"/&gt;                                 &lt;/i:EventTrigger&gt;                             &lt;/i:Interaction.Triggers&gt;                         &lt;/my:AutoCompleteTextBox&gt; </code></pre>  <p>And ViewModel:</p>  <pre><code>  public ICommand CityF5Command { get; set; }     CityF5Command = new CustomCommand(CityF5, CanCityF5);     private void CityF5(object obj)             {                 Messenger.Default.Send&lt;int&gt;(1);             } </code></pre>  <p>I`m out of ideas. </p>